===Example setup===
The aim is to maximise damage output while minimising risk. Choosing three items with a large amount of melee strength bonus is recommended, such as 
the [[ultor ring]] or the [[avernic defender]], and using cheap items otherwise which can be easily replaced such as [[barrows gloves]], [[Salve amulet (e)]], and the [[helm of Neitiznot]].

If on a [[skeleton]] or [[boss task]], the player can use [[bracelet of slaughter]] to extend the task. This will affect damage output, but lower the player's risk slightly.

