As Vet'ion is possible to defeat without taking any damage, supplies are mostly tailored to surviving PKers. Vet'ion frequently drops un-noted blighted food or potions that replace supplies used during the fight.

* [[Royal seed pod]] or any other level 30 [[Wilderness]] teleport. [[Ring of wealth|Ring of wealth (5)]] can be configured to be a one-click teleport to the [[Grand Exchange]] using [[menu entry swapper]].
* [[Divine super combat potion]]
* 4+ [[Blighted super restores]] or [[Prayer potions]] and 1+ [[Sanfew serum]]
* [[Saradomin brew]]s with [[blighted super restores]] for emergency food
* [[Looting bag]] (strongly recommended, can also be obtained from [[Vet'ion]] or his summons)
* Some form of [[antipoison]] e.g. [[Sanfew serums]] (optional, recommended, if poisoned/venomed by a PKer or inside the [[escape caves]])
* Rest food — [[Blighted manta ray]] or [[blighted anglerfish]] at 93+ {{SCP|Hitpoints|link=no}} (optional: 2+ [[Blighted karambwan]] for [[Food/Fast foods|combo-eating]])
